*** Settings ***
Documentation    Home Page keywords.
Resource         ../common.resource

*** Variables ***
${HOME_URL}         ${BASE_URL}/
${NAV_MENU}         id:navigation
${USER_PROFILE}     css:.user-profile
${LOGOUT_BUTTON}    id:logout-button
${SEARCH_INPUT}     id:search-input
${SEARCH_BUTTON}    id:search-button

*** Keywords ***
Navigate To Home Page
    [Documentation]    Open the home page and wait for the nav menu.
    Go To                           ${HOME_URL}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${NAV_MENU}    ${TIMEOUT}

Verify User Is Logged In
    [Documentation]    Assert that the user profile + logout button are visible.
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${USER_PROFILE}     ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Be Visible        ${LOGOUT_BUTTON}

Click Logout
    [Documentation]    Log the user out and wait for the profile to disappear.
    Wait And Click Element           ${LOGOUT_BUTTON}
    Wait Until Element Is Not Visible    ${USER_PROFILE}    ${TIMEOUT}

Search For
    [Arguments]    ${search_term}
    Wait And Input Text    ${SEARCH_INPUT}    ${search_term}
    Wait And Click Element    ${SEARCH_BUTTON}

Verify Navigation Menu Is Visible
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${NAV_MENU}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Be Visible        ${NAV_MENU}
